column5: Difficult province to spell, but according to Holdfast, an easy one to fish....I am looking forward to meeting you, sir. My flight leaves in 1.75 hrs D.V. and I am stoked for next weekend! This will be my last post for ~ 2 weeks, hopefully I will have some fish porn to post when I return from the rectangle province!
Have fun, catch big fish, and take lotsa pics!!!
Don't call me Sir because I work for a Living. LOL      Give me a call when you get settled
